section.def:
portable equipment (手提設備) means any fire service equipment which is manufactured, used or
            designed to be used as an independent unit for the purpose of extinguishing, attacking,
            preventing or limiting a fire;

paragraph.content:
a treatment centre as defined by section 2 of the Drug
                        Dependent Persons Treatment and Rehabilitation Centres (Licensing) Ordinance
                            (Cap. 566);
